<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.9.8">
<l>kulaiyārnta paḻukkāyum pacuṅkāyum pāḷaimuttum</l>
<l>talaiyārnta viḷaṅkamukiṉ taṭañcōlait tirunaṟaiyūr</l>
<l>malaiyārnta kōlañcēr maṇimāṭam mikamaṉṉi</l>
<l>nilaiyāra niṉṟāṉṟaṉ nīṭkaḻalē yaṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In Tirunaṟaiyūr with vast groves of young areca [trees] whose tops are filled</l>
<l>With clusters full of ripe fruit, green fruit, and kernels in bracts,</l>
<l>O heart, take refuge at the broad anklets of the one who stands steadily,</l>
<l>Being firmly established in the beautiful raised shrine with mountain-like contours.</l> 
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
